+    // TurboWasm: list / scalar buffer accessors for the GPU compute kernel
+    // pipeline (see gpu-kernel-spec-summary.md §6.1). These are non-
+    // breaking additions: callers without @compute regions simply never
+    // call them. They return a `{data, length, dtype}` triple where data
+    // is a freshly-allocated Float32Array / Int32Array / Uint8Array view
+    // mirroring the scratch-vm list, so the GPU side can call syncToHost
+    // after the dispatch. The `dtype` matches the @bind directive's dtype.
